data.description: Auction! Auction! Auction! This home will be sold with the Executive Home Auction Process that will be conducted through email on Monday afternoon. Spacious 4 bedroom / 3 bathroom family home that needs a little sprucing, in a highly desirable neighborhood with the highly desired Placentia-linda School district! Bring your big ideas this weekend. Big grassy park one block away with swings, slides and basketball court. Soaring cathedral ceilings, large master suite, downstairs bedroom and bath, large bonus room, cozy fireplace, bubbling spa, RV or boat parking, and so much more. Solar is fully paid off. This is a must see home!
